description:
First up on today’s Unqualifiedcalls:

…Anna, Sim, and Mark-Paul Gosselaar chat with Tim from Nevada who is struggling to understand why his in-laws have stopped taking an active role in his 3-year-old son, Milo’s, life.

Next, Unqualified travels back in time with a classic call from Ken Jeong’s episode:

…Anna, Sim, and Ken chat with Rebecca, a 23-year old recent college grad who is concerned about how her boyfriend’s upcoming med school plans will impact the future of their relationship.

Don’t forget to visit unqualified.com/contact to share your feedback – we love hearing from you!
